/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: MPS_USLUGE */
/*==============================================================*/
create table MPS_USLUGE
(
ID3 char(4) not null,
VO_OZNAKA char(2) null,
NAZIV varchar(30) not null,
CENA varchar(30) null,
OPIS varchar(1024) null,
constraint PK_MPS_USLUGE primary key (ID3)
);

/*==============================================================*/

);

);

on delete restrict;
